ge%20this%20year%20marked%20by%20searing%20heat%2C%20bringing%20the%20overall%20tally%20to%20more%20than%20600.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20confirmed%20around%2068%20dead...%20Some%20are%20because%20of%20natural%20causes%20and%20we%20had%20many%20old-age%20pilgrims.%20And%20some%20are%20due%20to%20the%20weather%20conditions%2C%20that's%20what%20we%20assume%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20diplomat%2C%20who%20spoke%20on%20condition%20of%20anonymity%2C%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20toll%20comes%20after%20two%20Arab%20diplomats%20told%20AFP%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20550%20deaths%20had%20been%20recorded%20during%20the%20hajj%2C%20one%20of%20the%20five%20pillars%20of%20Islam%20that%20all%20Muslims%20with%20the%20means%20must%20perform%20at%20least%20once.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20figure%20included%20323%20Egyptians%20and%2060%20Jordanians%2C%20the%20Arab%20diplomats%20said%2C%20and%20one%20specified%20that%20nearly%20all%20the%20Egyptians%20died%20%26quot%3Bbecause%20of%20heat%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFatalities%20have%20also%20been%20confirmed%20by%20Indonesia%2C%20Iran%2C%20Senegal%2C%20Tunisia%20and%20Iraq's%20autonomous%20Kurdistan%20region%2C%20though%20in%20many%20cases%20authorities%20have%20not%20specified%20the%20cause.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20total%20reported%20dead%20so%20far%20is%20645%2C%20according%20to%20an%20AFP%20tally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%20more%20than%20200%20pilgrims%20were%20reported%20dead%2C%20most%20of%20them%20from%20Indonesia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaudi%20Arabia%20has%20not%20provided%20information%20on%20fatalities%2C%20though%20it%20reported%20more%20than%202%2C700%20cases%20of%20%26quot%3Bheat%20exhaustion%26quot%3B%20on%20Sunday%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20diplomat%20who%20confirmed%20the%20Indian%20fatalities%20said%20there%20were%20also%20some%20Indian%20pilgrims%20missing%2C%20but%20he%20declined%20to%20provide%20an%20exact%20number.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20happens%20every%20year...