onducted%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20Education%20has%20ordered%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fugc-net-neet-row-education-emergency-net-scrapped-amid-neet-row-opposition-gets-new-ammo-5928689%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll%5C%22%3Ecancellation%20of%20the%20UGC-NET%20exam%3C%2Fa%3E%20conducted%20by%20the%20National%20Testing%20Agency%20(NTA)%2C%20just%20a%20day%20after%20it%20was%20held.%20Controversy%20has%20again%20erupted%20following%20the%20cancellation%20of%20the%20second%20entrance%20exam%20conducted%20by%20the%20NTA.%20The%20centre%20had%20earlier%20scrapped%C2%A0%20the%20grace%20marks%20awarded%20to%201%2C563%20candidates%20who%20took%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fneet-ug-2024-result-row-top-rankers-reduced-to-61-as-grace-marks-withdrawn-5882844%5C%22%3ENEET%20UG%202024%3C%2Fa%3E.%20A%20re-test%20has%20been%20scheduled%20for%20these%20students%20for%20June%2023%2C%202024%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20UGC-NET%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20National%20Testing%20Agency%20conducts%20the%20University%20Grants%20Commission%20%E2%80%93%20National%20Eligibility%20Test%20(UGC-NET)%20to%20screen%20eligible%20candidates%20for%20the%20post%20of%20Assistant%20Professor%2C%20Junior%20Research%20Fellowship%20and%20PhD%20admissions%20in%20Indian%20universities%20and%20colleges.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20exam%2C%20this%20year%2C%20was%20held%20in%20pen%20and%20paper%20mode%20on%20June%2018%2C%202024%20in%20two%20shifts.%20The%20first%20shift%20was%20conducted%20from%209.30%20am%20to%2012.30%20pm%20and%20the%20second%20shift%20from%203%20pm%20to%206%20pm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20order%20to%20regularise%20the%20UGC-NET%20examination%20cycle%2C%20the%20agency%20holds%20the%20UGC%20NET%20December%202023%20in%2083%20subjects%2C%20at%20selected%20cities%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20exam%20is%20held%20twice%20every%20year%20in%20the%20month%20of%20June%20and%20December.%20From%20December%202018%20onwards%2C%20UGC-NET%20was%20being%20held%20in%20Computer%20Based%20Test%20(CBT)%20mode.%20However%2C%20in%20a%20departure%20from%20previous%20practices%2C%20the%20exam%20was%20conducted%20in%20a%20pen-and-paper%20format%20this%20time.%20Approximately%2081%25%20of%20the%2011.21%20lakh%20registered%20candidates%20appeared%20for%20the%20exam%2C%20held%20in%20317%20cities%20nationwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECandidates%20are%20required%20to%20score%20an%20aggregate%20marks%20in%20Paper%201%20and%20Paper%202%20of%20UGC%20NET%20for%20awarding%20of%20Junior%20Research%20Fellowship%20(JRF)%20and%2F%20or%20eligibility%20for%20Assistant%20Professorship.%20Students%20who%20qualify%20the%20eligibility%20test%20for%20Assistant%20Professorship%20are%20governed%20by%20the%20rules%20and%20regulations%20of%20the%20concerned%20universities%2Fcolleges%2Fstate%20governments%2C%20as%20the%20case%20may%20be%20for%20recruitment%20of%20Assistant%20Professor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20candidates%20qualifying%20under%20the%20%E2%80%98appointment%20as%20Assistant%20Professor%20and%20admission%20to%20PhD'%20category%20will%20be%20eligible%20for%20appointment%20as%20Assistant%20Professor%20and%20admission%20to%20PhD%20but%20not%20for%20the%20award%20of%20JRF.%20Similarly%2C%20students%20qualifying%20under%20the%20%E2%80%98admission%20to%20PhD%20only'%20category%20will%20be%20eligible%20for%20admission%20to%20PhD%20only%20but%20not%20for%20the%20award%20of%20JRF%20and%2For%20appointment%20as%20Assistant%20Professor.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718861160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fqmf5uoto_csirugc-net-june-2024-_625x300_02_May_24.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fwhat-is-ugc-net-exam-and-why-is-it-conducted-5928819%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20exam%20was%20held%20in%20pen%20and%20paper%20mode%20on%20June%2018%2C%202024%20in%20two%20shifts.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fwhat-is-ugc-net-exam-and-why-is-it-conducted-5928819%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fwhat-is-ugc-net-exam-and-why-is-it-conducted-5928819%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fwhat-is-ugc-net-exam-and-why-is-it-conducted-5928819%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rs%201.2%20Lakh%20Fine%20Each%20On%20IIT%20Bombay%20Students%20Over%20%26quot%3BRamayana%26quot%3B%20Play%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20(IIT)%20Bombay%20has%20fined%20eight%20students%20for%20staging%20a%20controversial%20play%20titled%20'Raahovan%2C'%20believed%20to%20be%20a%20parody%20of%20Ramayana%2C%20during%20the%20institute's%20Performing%20Arts%20Festival%20(PAF)%20on%20March%2031.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20section%20of%20students%20had%20formally%20complained%20against%20the%20play%2C%20alleging%20that%20it%20was%20loosely%20based%20on%20the%20revered%20Hindu%20epic%20Ramayana%20and%20had%20derogatory%20references%20to%20Hindu%20beliefs%20and%20deities.%20Some%20students%20alleged%20that%20the%20play%20lampooned%20the%20lead%20characters%20and%20mocked%20cultural%20values%20in%20the%20guise%20of%20%26quot%3Bpromoting%20feminism%26quot%3B.%20The%20complaints%20led%20to%20a%20disciplinary%20committee%20meeting%20on%20May%208%2C%20resulting%20in%20the%20penalties%20announced%20on%20June%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20institute%20imposed%20fines%20of%20Rs%201.2%20lakh%20each%20on%20four%20students%20-%20the%20amount%20is%20almost%20the%20same%20as%20a%20semester's%20tuition%20fee.%20Four%20other%20students%20were%20fined%20Rs%2040%2C000%20each.%20Graduating%20students%20faced%20additional%20sanctions%2C%20including%20a%20ban%20from%20the%20institute's%20gymkhana%20awards%20given%20to%20students.%20Junior%20students%20were%20debarred%20from%20hostel%20facilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20penalties%20are%20due%20on%20July%2020%2C%202024%2C%20at%20the%20office%20of%20the%20Dean%20of%20Student%20Affairs.%20The%20institute%20warned%20that%20any%20breach%20of%20this%20penalty%20would%20result%20in%20further%20sanctions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20controversy%20gained%20traction%20on%20social%20media%20when%20the%20'IIT%20B%20for%20Bharat'%20group%20denounced%20the%20play%20on%20April%208%2C%20citing%20it%20as%20a%20mockery%20of%20Lord%20Ram%20and%20the%20Ramayana.%20The%20group%20posted%20video%20clips%20from%20the%20performance%2C%20alleging%20that%20the%20students%20misused%20academic%20freedom%20to%20ridicule%20revered%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20videos%20that%20went%20viral%20on%20the%20internet%20show%20students%20presenting%20a%20play%20allegedly%20inspired%20by%20Ramayana%20characters%20and%20plot%20settings.%20In%20one%20video%2C%20a%20student%2C%20allegedly%20playing%20Sita%2C%20praises%20her%20%26quot%3Bkidnapper%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20place%20she%20was%20taken%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20welcome%20the%20disciplinary%20action%20taken%20by%20the%20IIT%20Bombay%20administration%20against%20those%20involved%20in%20the%20play%20'Raahovan%2C'%20which%20depicted%20the%20Ramayana%20in%20a%20derogatory%20manner%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20group%20stated%20on%20social%20media%20platform%20X.%20%26quot%3BWe%20urge%20the%20administration%20to%20establish%20guidelines%20to%20ensure%20that%20no%20religion%20is%20ridiculed%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20freedom%20of%20expression%20on%20campus.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20certain%20groups%20appreciated%20the%20institution's%20decision%20to%20initiate%20disciplinary%20action%20against%20the%20students%2C%20some%20have%20condemned%20it%20as%20an%20attack%20on%20freedom%20of%20expression.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20always%20heard%20that%20educational%20institutions%20should%20be%20safe%20spaces%2C%20safe%20for%20voicing%20opinions.%20Alas%2C%20even%20IITs%20are%20no%20longer%20safe%20spaces%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20one%20person%20on%20X.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20egregious.%20Students%20cannot%20be%20fined%20in%20colleges%20for%20being%20disrespectful%20to%20any%20religion.%20Colleges%20are%20places%20where%20one%20should%20be%20able%20to%20freely%20mock%20religion.%20IIT%20Bombay%20must%20take%20this%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20another.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Performing%20Arts%20Festival%20is%20an%20annual%20cultural%20event%20at%20IIT%20Bombay%2C%20known%20for%20showcasing%20student%20talent%20in%20various%20art%20forms.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718860980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fo58dr6qg_iit-bombay-raahovan-_625x300_20_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frs-1-2-lakh-fine-each-on-iit-bombay-students-over-ramayana-play-5928839%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20(IIT)%20Bombay%20has%20fined%20eight%20students%20for%20staging%20a%20controversial%20play%20titled%20'Raahovan%2C'%20believed%20to%20be%20a%20parody%20of%20Ramayana%2C%20during%20the%20institute's%20Performing%20Arts%20Festival%20(PAF)%20on%20March%2031.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frs-1-2-lakh-fine-each-on-iit-bombay-students-over-ramayana-play-5928839%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frs-1-2-lakh-fine-each-on-iit-bombay-students-over-ramayana-play-5928839%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frs-1-2-lakh-fine-each-on-iit-bombay-students-over-ramayana-play-5928839%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22George%20Santos%20says%20he's%20now%20on%20OnlyFans%2C%20but%20he's%20there%20to%20'stir%20the%20pot'%20and%20not%20to%20post%20'adult%20content'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20widt