allegedly%20over%20paper%20leak%20reports.%20The%20decision%20follows%20a%20massive%20controversy%20surrounding%20the%20NEET%20medical%20entrance%20exam%2C%20which%20is%20currently%20under%20Supreme%20Court%20review.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20departure%20from%20previous%20years%2C%20the%20National%20Eligibility%20Test%20(NET)%20was%20conducted%20in%20a%20pen-and-paper%20format%20this%20time.%20Approximately%2081%25%20of%20the%2011.21%20lakh%20registered%20candidates%20appeared%20for%20the%20exam%20held%20in%20317%20cities%20nationwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20education%20ministry%20cited%20inputs%20that%20the%20integrity%20of%20the%20exam%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Bcompromised%26quot%3B%2C%20received%20from%20the%20National%20Cyber%20Crime%20Threat%20Analytics%20Unit%20of%20the%20Indian%20Cyber%20Crime%20Coordination%20Centre%20(I4C).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20ensure%20the%20highest%20level%20of%20transparency%20and%20sanctity%20of%20the%20examination%20process%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Education%2C%20Government%20of%20India%20has%20decided%20that%20the%20UGC-NET%20June%202024%20Examination%20be%20cancelled%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ministry%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20fresh%20examination%20shall%20be%20conducted%2C%20for%20which%20information%20shall%20be%20shared%20separately.%20Simultaneously%2C%20the%20matter%20is%20being%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(C.B.I.)%20for%20thorough%20investigation%20in%20the%20matter%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbout%20the%20UGC-NET%20exam%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UGC-NET%20exam%20assesses%20Indian%20nationals%20for%20eligibility%20as%20'Assistant%20Professor'%20and%20for%20'Junior%20Research%20Fellowship%20and%20Assistant%20Professor'%20roles%20in%20universities%20and%20colleges.%20It%20is%20typically%20conducted%20by%20the%20NTA%20in%20Computer-Based%20Test%20(CBT)%20mode%20twice%20annually%20(June%20and%20December).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECandidates%20qualifying%20for%20Assistant%20Professorship%20are%20considered%20based%20on%20their%20performance%20in%20Paper-I%20and%20Paper-II%20of%20the%20UGC-NET%20exam.%20Those%20eligible%20for%20Junior%20Research%20Fellowship%20(JRF)%20can%20pursue%20research%20or%20apply%20for%20Assistant%20Professorship.%20Rules%20for%20Assistant%20Professors%20vary%20by%20university%2C%20college%2C%20or%20state%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cancellation%20and%20subsequent%20investigation%20mark%20a%20significant%20development%20in%20the%20examination%20process%2C%20impacting%20thousands%20of%20aspirants%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718860920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fuoe0vapg_exam-generic-pixabay_625x300_17_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fugc-net-exam-explained-why-ugc-net-exam-was-cancelled-a-day-after-it-was-conducted-5928286%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Ministry%20of%20Education%20has%20ordered%20the%20cancellation%20of%20the%20UGC-NET%20exam%20conducted%20by%20the%20National%20Testing%20Agency%20(NTA)%2C%20just%20a%20day%20after%20it%20took%20place.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fugc-net-exam-explained-why-ugc-net-exam-was-cancelled-a-day-after-it-was-conducted-5928286%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fugc-net-exam-explained-why-ugc-net-exam-was-cancelled-a-day-after-it-was-conducted-5928286%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fugc-net-exam-explained-why-ugc-net-exam-was-cancelled-a-day-after-it-was-conducted-5928286%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Stock%20Market%20LIVE%20updates%3A%20Mid%2C%20small-cap%20stocks%20outperform%20benchmarks%3B%20Map%20My%20India%20soars%2014%25%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2