B%22title%22%3A%22Fraud%2C%20Mental%20Torture%20And%20Rape%3A%20Bihar's%20Call%20Centre%20From%20Hell%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFor%20months%2C%20Bihar's%20Muzaffarpur%20was%20home%20to%20a%20call%20centre%20from%20hell.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20company%20called%20DBR%20Networking%20had%20put%20up%20advertisements%20across%20social%20media%2C%20including%20Facebook%2C%20seeking%20agents%20for%20a%20call%20centre%20run%20by%20them.%20The%20catch%3A%20the%20applicants%20had%20to%20be%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20soon%20as%20a%20woman%20would%20apply%2C%20police%20officials%20said%2C%20they%20would%20be%20shown%20dreams%20of%20a%20bright%20future%20and%20then%20be%20asked%20to%20pay%20Rs%2020%2C000%20to%20undergo%20training%20for%20the%20job%2C%20for%20which%20they%20would%20be%20asked%20to%20go%20to%20Muzaffarpur.%20The%20training%20would%20begin%20soon%20after%2C%20but%20so%20would%20a%20cycle%20of%20mental%20torture%2C%20fraud%20and%2C%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20even%20rape%20and%20forced%20abortions%2C%20said%20an%20official.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20First%20Information%20Report%20(FIR)%20filed%20by%20one%20of%20the%20survivors%20on%20June%202%2C%20she%20fell%20for%20the%20advertisement%2C%20thinking%20it%20was%20genuine%2C%20and%20reached%20the%20company's%20centre%20in%20Muzaffarpur%2C%20where%20there%20were%20around%20150%20women%20like%20her.%20She%20said%20she%20got%20in%20touch%20with%20one%20of%20the%20accused%2C%20Tilak%20Kumar%20Singh%2C%20and%20she%20and%20all%20the%20other%20women%20were%20trained%20to%20make%20calls%20and%20trick%20people%20into%20falling%20for%20scams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20women%20were%20mentally%20tortured%20when%20they%20failed%20to%20meet%20their%20targets%20and%20the%20survivor%20who%20filed%20the%20FIR%20said%20she%20was%20raped%20when%20she%20missed%20hers.%20She%20alleged%20that%20Tilak%20Kumar%20Singh%20forced%20her%20to%20have%20sex%20with%20her%20on%20multiple%20occasions%20and%20then%20made%20her%