including%20Health%20Minister%20Ma%20Subramaniam%2C%20to%20rush%20to%20Kallakurichi%20and%20ensure%20every%20possible%20medical%20help%20to%20the%20affected%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDisturbing%20reports%20started%20emerging%20yesterday%20after%20three%20people%20died%20in%20different%20locations%20over%20the%20past%20three%20days.%20Despite%20a%20buzz%20that%20the%20deaths%20may%20have%20been%20caused%20by%20toxic%20liquor%2C%20District%20Collector%20Sravan%20Kumar%20Jatavath%20initially%20denied%20such%20reports.%20%26quot%3BThese%20deaths%20have%20happened%20over%20three%20days.%20One%20of%20them%20was%20a%20teetotaller%20and%20one%20of%20them%20had%20a%20stomach%20problem.%20No%20one%20died%20in%20the%20hospital%2C%20and%20none%20came%20in%20an%20inebriated%20condition.%20In%20the%20commotion%2C%20someone%20said%20illicit%20liquor%20and%20it%20spread.%20We%20are%20investigating%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20tragedy%20is%20being%20seen%20as%20a%20huge%20failure%20by%20intelligence%20agencies%20and%20the%20prohibition%20enforcement%20wing.%20Last%20year%2C%20too%2C%2022%20people%20died%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20after%20consuming%20methanol.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAIADMK%20chief%20and%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20in%20the%20Assembly%20Edappadi%20K%20Palaniswami%20slammed%20the%20ruling%20DMK%20for%20and%20said%20the%20state%20government%20failed%20to%20curb%20the%20toxic%20liquor%20problem%20even%20after%20he%20pointed%20out.%20%26quot%3BI%20urge%20Chief%20Minister%20M%20K%20Stalin%20to%20take%20stringent%20action%20to%20curb%20toxic%20liquor%20instead%20of%20word%20play%20like%20last%20time%2C%20when%20they%20called%20it%20methanol%20and%20not%20toxic%20liquor.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EState%20BJP%20chief%20K%20Annamalai%20said%20DMK%20had%20not%20%26quot%3Blearnt%20its%20lesson%26quot%3B%20after%2022%20deaths%20due%20to%20consumption%20of%20toxic%20liquor%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGovernor%20R%20N%20Ravi%2C%20whose%20tenure