t%20before%20the%20Brenner%20Pass%20over%20the%20Europabr%C3%BCcke%20bridge%20towards%20Italy.%3Cp%3EKarl-Josef%20Hildenbrand%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETraffic%20deaths%20have%20spiked%20in%20certain%20places%20around%20the%20world%20in%20recent%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAustria%20is%20trying%20to%20do%20something%20about%20it%2C%20recently%20passing%20a%20law%20to%20deter%20'super%20speeders.'%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EEuropean%20countries%20tend%20to%20have%20stricter%20traffic%20rules%20and%2C%20as%20a%20result%2C%20safer%20roads.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Austrian%20government%20is%20cracking%20down%20on%20%26quot%3Bsuper%20speeders%26quot%3B%20on%20its%20roads%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20boost%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zdf.de%2Fnachrichten%2Fpanorama%2Foesterreich-raser-verkehr-strafe-100.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20law%3C%2Fa%3E%20allows%20the%20government%20to%20confiscate%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20even%20sell%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0the%20vehicles%20of%20those%20who%20drive%2060%20kilometers%20per%20hour%20(about%2037%20mph)%20or%20more%20over%20the%20speed%20limit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20the%20US%2C%20Austria%20has%20seen%20a%20recent%20uptick%20in%20road%20deaths.%20But%20roads%20are%20far%20safer%20in%20the%20European%20nation%20than%20in%20the%20US%2C%20which%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F01%2F10%2Fmagazine%2Fdangerous-driving.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efar%20deadlier%20roads%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20other%20rich%20countries.%20The%20US%20has%20seen%20road%20deaths%20spike%20recently%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0in%202021%2C%20traffic%20fatalities%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2022%2F05%2F17%2Fus-traffic-deaths-hit-16-year-high-in-2021-dot-says.html%23%3A~%3Atext%3DU.S.%2520traffic%2520deaths%2520reached%2520a%2C2021%252C%2520according%2520to%2520government%2520estimates%26amp%3Btext%3DNHTSA%252C%2520a%2520federal%2520vehicle%2520safety%2Chave%2520died%2520during%2520a%2520crash.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehit%20a%2016-year%20high%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20in%202023%2C%20deaths%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Ftanyamohn%2F2024%2F02%2F27%2Ftraffic-crash-deaths-in-2023-remain-at-devastatingly-high-level%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E13.6%25%20higher%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAustria's%20director%20general%20of%20transportation%2C%20Vera%20Hofbauer%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2024-06-19%2Faustria-aims-to-curb-crashes-with-crackdown-on-super-speeders%3Fsrnd%3Dall%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20Bloomberg%20News%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20new%20law%20hasn't%20been%20on%20the%20books%20for%20long%20enough%20to%20measure%20its%20impact%2C%20but%20it's%20already%20being%20felt.%20Just%20hours%20after%20the%20law%20went%20into%20effect%2C%20the%20government%20confiscated%20the%20car%20of%20a%20super%20speeder%2C%20she%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAustria%20experienced%204.1%20road%20deaths%20for%20every%20100%2C000%20people%20in%202022.%20Hofbauer%20argued%20that%20%26quot%3Bdrastic%20measures%26quot%3B%20must%20be%20taken%20to%20stop%20drivers%20who%20%26quot%3Bare%20using%20their%20car%20like%20a%20weapon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAustrian%20officials%20aren't%20alone%20in%20cracking%20down%20on%20dangerous%20driving.%20A%20slew%20of%20European%20countries%20have%20implemented%20the%20world's%20strictest%20road%20safety%20regulations.%20In%20several%20countries%2C%20speeding%20tickets%20are%20calculated%20based%20on%20the%20driver's%20income%2C%20so%20the%20wealthier%20the%20driver%20is%2C%20the%20steeper%20the%20fine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Switzerland%2C%20speeding%20tickets%20have%20been%20calculated%20based%20on%20both%20income%20and%20wealth%20since%202007%2C%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fid%2Fwbna3