%3EIt%20had%20everything%20a%20wedding%20needed%3A%20two%20people%20in%20love%2C%20happy%20families%2C%20loads%20of%20joy%2C%20scrumptious%20food%2C%20and%20abundant%20happiness.%20What%20it%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20was%20plastic%20or%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F291582%2Fplan-green-eco-friendly-indian-wedding-with-ebikes-cycles-in-delhi%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunnecessary%20waste%20%3C%2Fa%3Eof%20any%20kind%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20food%2C%20plastic%2C%20or%20paper.%20The%20beauty%20of%20the%20union%20was%20enhanced%20by%20the%20simplicity%20of%20the%20setting%2C%20surrounded%20by%20coconut%20trees%2C%20areca%20palms%2C%20mangoes%2C%20and%20lush%20greenery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20everything%20the%20bride%20had%20dreamed%20of%20since%20she%20was%20a%20little%20girl!%20Whenever%20anyone%20asked%20Poorvi%2C%20a%20nutritionist%20and%20naturopath%2C%20what%20she%20wanted%20for%20her%20big%20day%2C%20her%20answer%20remained%20the%20same%20over%20the%20years%3A%20a%20simple%2C%20eco-friendly%20wedding%20at%20her%20family%20farm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20decided%20to%20marry%20her%20husband%2C%20an%20organic%20farmer%2C%20his%20family%20readily%20agreed%20to%20her%20non-negotiable%20requirement%20of%20a%20sustainable%20wedding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FCover-image-33-1718768243.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20sugarcane%20mantapa%20doubled%20up%20as%20a%20meal%20for%20the%20cows!%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FCover-image-33-1718768243.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FCover-image-33-1718768243-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A