e-in-crores-ready-to-eat-food-health-sutra-hyderabad%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Equit%20his%20job%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20devote%20all%20his%20time%20to%20training%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20Hetal%20recounts.%20How%20tough%20was%20it%20to%20take%20this%20life-altering%20decision%20on%20the%20spur%20of%20the%20moment%3F%20Sudhir%20responds%2C%20%E2%80%9CHumans%20have%20crazy%20minds%20and%20when%20the%20mind%20decides%20it%20wants%20something%2C%20nothing%20is%20an%20obstacle%20anymore.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPiecing%20the%20story%20together%20of%20how%20she%20went%20from%20being%20a%20child%20who%20was%20an%20ace%20in%20judo%20(Japanese%20martial%20arts)%20to%20putting%20India%20on%20the%20sumo%20wrestling%20map%2C%20she%20says%20her%20parents%20have%20always%20been%20her%20biggest%20inspiration%20and%20cheerleaders.%20In%20fact%2C%20she%20says%2C%20she%20gets%20her%20love%20for%20sports%20from%20them.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20in%20my%20DNA.%20My%20parents%20lived%20in%20a%20village%20all%20their%20lives.%20So%2C%20in%20many%20ways%2C%20sport%20was%20a%20big%20part%20of%20their%20lives.%20And%20when%20I%20was%20five%20years%20old%2C%20it%20became%20a%20big%20part%20of%20mine%20too.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fhetal-dave-1718375371.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hetal%20Dave%2C%20India's%20only%20professional%20female%20sumo%20wrestler%20with%20her%20mother%2C%20father%20and%20brother%2C%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fhetal-dave-1718375371.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fhetal-dave-1718375371-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fhetal-dave-1718375371-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20htt