aption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAamore%20exported%20its%20mangoes%20to%20London%2C%20Canada%2C%20the%20United%20States%2C%20and%20Kuwait.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20this%2C%20300%20small%20landholding%20farmers%20from%20Jagar%20%E2%80%93%20who%20were%20dependent%20on%20middlemen%20for%20generations%20%E2%80%93%20came%20together%20and%20launched%20a%20direct-to-consumer%20(D2C)%20brand%20Aamor%C3%A9%20(Italian%20word%20for%20love)%2C%20to%20make%20people%20abroad%20fall%20in%20love%20with%20authentic%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2Fweb-stories%2Fmost-expensive-mangoes-in-india-alphonso-miyazaki-noorjahan-kohitur-sindhri%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAlphonso%20mangoes%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOwned%20by%20smallholder%20farmers%2C%20the%20brand%20exported%2010%20tonnes%20of%20its%20produce%20to%20London%2C%20Canada%2C%20the%20United%20States%2C%20and%20Kuwait%20by%20air.%20More%20exports%20meant%20more%20profits%20and%20happier%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20bitter%20tale%20behind%20the%20sweet%20tidings%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETejas%20grew%20up%20relishing%20Alphonsos%2C%20locally%20called%20%3Cem%3EHapus%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20on%20his%20two-acre%20farm.%20While%20savouring%20the%20sweet%20fruit%2C%20he%20also%20saw%20what%20went%20behind%20cultivating%20this%20popular%20fruit%20variety.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20had%20seen%20my%20father%20toiling%20in%20the%20field.%20The%20process%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2Fweb-stories%2Fmango-farmer-maharashtra-kakasaheb-sawant-kesar-hapus-chikoo-custard-apple-earns-crore%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrowing%20%3Cem%3EHapus%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3Eis%20cumbersome.%20In%20our%20region%2C%20the%20soil%20is%20mainly%20lateritic%20and%20rocky%2C%20and%20mangoes%20are%20grown%20under%20rain-fed%20conditions.%20My%20father%20would%20first%20break%20the%20rocky%20soil%20and%20make%20the%20field%20favourable%20for%20mango%20plantation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COnce%20the%20fruiting%20started%2C%20he%20would%20be%20out%20all%20day%20in%20summer%20heat%20protecting%20them%20from%20monkey%20attacks.%20If%20you%20are%20out%20of%20sight%20for%20even%20a%20few%20minutes%2C%20monkeys%20pluck%20the%20fruits%20and%20destroy%20the%20plantation.%20Farmers%20need%20to%20be%20very%20careful%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Tejas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FAamore-1-1718354143.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22As%20many%20as%20300%20small%20farmers%20took%20a%20bold%20step%20of%20taking%20Alphonsos%20to%20the%20global%20stage.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FAamore-1-1718354143.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FAamore-1-1718354143-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FAamore-1-1718354143-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FAamore-1-1718354143-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FAamore-1-1718354143-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-353063%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAs%20many%20as%20300%20small%20farmers%20took%20a%20bold%20step%20of%20taking%20Alphonsos%20to%20the%20global%20stage.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20months%20of%20backbreaking%20work%2C%20farmers%20like%20Tejas%E2%80%99s%20father%20would%20hardly%20earn%20any%20decent%20incomes%20for%20their%20produce.%20%E2%80%9CFarmers%20usually%20sold%20their%20mangoes%20in%20Pune%20and%20APMC%20%3Cem%3Emandi%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20Vashi%20%E2%80%93%20the%20largest%20agricultural%20market%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20where%20they%20are%20forced%20to%20sell%20produce%20via%20middlemen.%20This%20is%20how%20the%20industry%20works%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20scope%20of%20exploitation%20in%20this%20industry.%20Middlemen%20would%20sell%20our%20produce%20for%20Rs%20800-900%20per%20dozen%20but%20the%20growers%20would%20get%20only%20Rs%20200.%20We%20were%20being%20cheated%20and%20this%20has%20been%20in%20place%20for%20generations!%E2%80%9D%20says%20Tejas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2028-year-old%20wanted%20to%20find%20a%20solution%20that%20put%20an%20end%20to%20this%20age-old%20agony.%20%E2%80%9COnce%2C%20while%20watching%20the%20news%2C%20I%20came%20to%20know%20that%20Maharashtra%20only%20exports%20five%20percent%20of%20its%20Alphonsos%20whereas%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20bulk%20produce%20is%20consumed%20in%20the%20state%20itself.%20After%20studying%2C%20we%20found%20out%20that%20we%20could%20earn%20handsomely%20if%20we%20entered%20the%20export%20market%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20consulting%20with%20a%20bunch%20of%20farmers%2C%20Tejas%20went%20on%20to%20form%20Konkan%20Ratnagiri%20Boomi%20Agro%20Producer%20Limited%2C%20which%20was%20formally%20launched%20in%20December%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhen%20small%20farmers%20unite%20against%20big%20players%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEntering%20the%20export%20business%20was%20a%20bold%20step%20for%20small%20farmers.%20%E2%80%9CInitially%2C%20it%20was%20difficult%20to%20understand%20flight%20bookings%2C%20transportation%2C%20various%20kinds%20of%20food%20licences%2C%20and%20MRL%20(maximum%20residue%20level)%20tests%20for%20crops.%20As%20local%20farmers%2C%20we%20lacked%20that%20much%20knowledge%20and%20awareness.%20Many%20farmers%20f