s%20from%20various%20witnesses%2C%20including%20women%20who%20claimed%20to%20have%20been%20exploited%20by%20the%20Maharaj.%20These%20testimonies%20were%20crucial%20in%20substantiating%20Karsandas%E2%80%99%20allegations%20and%20painted%20a%20stark%20picture%20of%20the%20abuses%20of%20power%20within%20the%20sect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20came%20to%20a%20close%20on%2022%20April%2C%201862%2C%20with%20a%20judgment%20in%20favour%20of%20Karsandas%20Mulji.%20The%20court%20awarded%20him%20Rs%2011%2C500%2C%20as%20he%20had%20to%20bear%20a%20total%20expenditure%20of%20Rs%2014%2C000%20during%20the%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClosing%20the%20case%20Judge%20Arnould%20stated%3A%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20not%20a%20question%20of%20theology%20that%20has%20been%20before%20us!%20It%20is%20a%20question%20of%20morality.%20The%20principle%20for%20which%20the%20defendant%20and%20his%20witnesses%20have%20been%20contending%20is%20simply%20this%3A%20That%20what%20is%20morally%20wrong%20cannot%20be%20theologically%20right.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarsandas%20passed%20away%20in%201871%20and%20is%20remembered%20fondly%20as%20the%20social%20reformer-journalist%20for%20his%20journalistic%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%20%26amp%3B%20Pranita%20Bhat)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tandfonline.com%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1080%2F00856401.2015.1050161%3Fscroll%3Dtop%26needAccess%3Dtrue%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EH%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tandfonline.com%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1080%2F00856401.2015.1050161%3Fscroll%3Dtop%26needAccess%3Dtrue%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eow%20to%20Defame%20a%20God%3