e%20plants%20don%E2%80%99t%20work%20in%20the%20long%20run%20for%20a%20variety%20of%20reasons%20including%20biological%20disturbance%2C%20equipment%20failure%20like%20burnt%20pumps%2C%20or%20the%20choking%20of%20membrane%20filters%20that%20act%20as%20a%20barrier%20to%20separate%20contaminants%20from%20the%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20is%20there%20a%20way%20for%20these%20plants%20to%20anticipate%20these%20problems%20and%20fix%20them%20in%20advance%20to%20improve%20their%20efficiency%20and%20longevity%3F%20Suffice%20it%20to%20say%20that%20there%20are%20a%20variety%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2Ftopics%2Fstartup%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndian%20startups%3C%2Fa%3E%20today%20that%20are%20developing%20technological%20solutions%20for%20wastewater%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIndia%20has%20about%2090%2C000%20installed%20wastewater%20treatment%20plants.%20But%20today%2095%25%20of%20the%20market%20is%20managed%20entirely%20manually%20by%20deploying%20operators%20in%20each%20plant.%20This%20has%20several%20drawbacks%3B%20problems%20are%20detected%20about%20three%20weeks%20late%20after%20breakdowns%20and%20operators%20lack%20the%20expertise%20to%20tackle%20problems.%20Other%20technologies%20in%20the%20market%20only%20make%20dents%20in%20part%20of%20the%20problem%3B%20they%20only%20monitor%20data%20or%20automate%20the%20key%20equipment%20like%20pumps%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20months%20of%20brainstorming%20to%20understand%20how%20they%20can%20solve%20this%20problem%20in%20a%20scalable%20manner%2C%20they%20started%20Digital%20Paani%20in%20end%202020%2C%20piloted%20an%20IoT-enabled%20software%20that%20manages%20end-to-end%20operations%20of%20a%20water%20treatment%20plant%2C%20and%20saw%20%E2%80%9Cincredible%20results%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDigital%20Paani%20is%20helping%20buildings%20and%20industries%20move%20towards%20water%20neutrality%20and%20reduce%20water%20losses%20across%20their%20campus.%20To%20do%20this%2C%20Digital%20Paani%20works%20in%20a%20stepwise%20manner%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1)%20Maximise%20recycling%20by%20ensuring%20wastewater%20infrastructure%20is%20working%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2)%20Helping%20industries%20and%20residential%20societies%20do%20water%20accounting%20real-time%2C%20know%20where%20they%20are%20having%20water%20losses%2C%20and%20provide%20roadmaps%20to%20reduce%20those%20losses.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3)%20Actually%20reducing%20those%20losses%20by%20providing%20operational%20excellence%20and%20management%20through%20technology%20for%20key%20assets%20contributing%20to%20water%20losses%20such%20as%20cooling%20towers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20Digital%20Paani%20is%20a%20water%20management%20platform%20that%20tracks%20and%20manages%20a%20water%20treatment%20plant%E2%80%99s%20health%20and%20performs%20tasks%20like%20equipment%20automation%2C%20providing%20WhatsApp%20updates%20to%20users%2C%20and%20guiding%20process%20management.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20offering%20real-time%20insights%2C%20complete%20control%2C%20and%2024%2F7%20management%20with%20actionable%20recommendations%2C%20they%20drive%20operational%20excellence%20for%20sustainable%20water%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Mansi%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CThink%20of%20our%20platform%20as%20a%20doctor%20for%20water%20infrastructure%2C%20telling%20buildings%20what%E2%80%99s%20wrong%20with%20their%20infrastructure%20and%20what%20it%20needs%2C%20as%20well%20as%20providing%20the%20medicine%20to%20fix%20it%2C%20whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20directing%20technicians%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F344518%2Ffind-missing-children-raju-nepali-duars-express-mail-ngo-rescues-trafficked-children-counselling%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWhatsApp%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20the%20right%20amount%20of%20chemical%20do