ing%20yes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20initially%20began%20by%20modifying%20traditional%20plastic%20grow%20bags%2C%20making%20holes%20to%20add%20water.%20However%2C%20these%20bags%20didn%E2%80%99t%20last%20long.%20After%20months%20of%20trials%2C%20he%20found%20his%20solution%20in%20silpaulin%20%E2%80%94%20a%20durable%2C%20waterproof%20material.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Feyyo-3-min-1718113042.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Eyyo%20with%20his%20patented%20grow%20bag%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Feyyo-3-min-1718113042.jpeg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Feyyo-3-min-1718113042-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Feyyo-3-min-1718113042-500x375.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Feyyo-3-min-1718113042-768x576.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Feyyo-3-min-1718113042-150x113.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-352693%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EEyyo%20with%20his%20patented%20grow%20bag.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20the%20bag%20to%20thrive%20in%20all%20weather%20conditions%20while%20keeping%20pests%20at%20bay.%20Grow%20bags%20are%20one%20of%20the%20most%20effective%20methods%20to%20grow%20vegetables%20and%20I%20wanted%20to%20make%20it%20even%20better.%20I%20designed%20the%20bag%20in%20such%20a%20way%20that%20it%20needs%20less%20water%20and%20provides%20a%20good%20harvest%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Eyyo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rectangular%20grow%20bag%20features%20two%20large%20holes%20on%20the