%20incomes%20of%20farmers.%C2%A0The%20venture%20earned%20a%20turnover%20of%20Rs%2050%20crore%20in%20the%20last%20financial%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGetting%20farmers%20the%20right%20value%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20one-and-a-half%20year-long%20stint%20with%20the%20soybean%20farmers%20in%20Rajasthan%20opened%20his%20eyes%20to%20their%20myriad%20problems.%20It%20also%20enabled%20him%20to%20come%20up%20with%20the%20most%20pressing%20problem%20that%20he%20intended%20to%20solve%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%20industry%20knows%20where%20they%20are%20sourcing%20their%20raw%20materials%20or%20parts%20from.%20They%20can%20trace%20back%20the%20origin%20in%20case%20of%20any%20issues.%20This%20is%20not%20possible%20in%20case%20of%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F310667%2Fvarun-khurana-iit-delhi-agritech-startup-otipy-helps-small-farmers-raise-income-sell-fresh-produce%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eagricultural%20supply%20chain%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlmost%20every%20stakeholder%20in%20this%20value%20chain%2C%20from%20the%20processor%20to%20the%20financial%20institutions%20to%20the%20policy%20makers%2C%20have%20this%20problem.%20Since%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20where%20it%E2%80%99s%20coming%20from%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20difficult%20to%20create%20a%20system%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Aneesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201000px)%20100vw%2C%201000px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FGram-Unnati-1718021978.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gram%20Unnati%20employees%20visit%20farmers%20every%20week%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FGram-Unnati-1718021978.jpeg%201000w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2F